WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.600
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:03.580
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.970 --> 00:00:07.390
I have some things on my heart to talk to y'all about.

00:00:07.390 --> 00:00:09.467
I haven't done a video in a week.

00:00:09.733 --> 00:00:12.773
The Lord told me, "I want you to seek me.

00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:16.836
" I said, "Well, Lord, I have to make videos for the people.

00:00:16.836 --> 00:00:19.600
" And he said, "Am I in charge of the channel or are you?

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.820
" And I said, "Well, you are, of course.

00:00:21.820 --> 00:00:26.480
" So he said, "I want you to pray and I want you to get filled back up.

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:31.080
" He said, "You cannot minister to the people out of your reserves.

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:36.600
You have to make sure you pray and minister to the people in your overflow.

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:57.700
" It was just time for me to fill myself back up, getting in prayer and getting back to that secret place with him, not worrying about everything, seeking him for what's coming, and abiding in him and him abiding with me.

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:00.075
It's been a beautiful time.

00:01:00.631 --> 00:01:16.700
I miss him because the distractions from so many things pulling on you all the time prevent you from taking that time and saying, "I refuse to allow things to keep pulling on me.

00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:20.799
I'm going to separate myself, not look at anything.

00:01:20.799 --> 00:01:23.424
I'm just going to focus on my relationship.

00:01:23.808 --> 00:01:35.000
" It was interesting because even last night I called my wife out there while I was sitting outside on our back porch and I said, "Look at the trees because they are getting ready to start changing.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:42.759
You can see the signs and the beauty of life.

00:01:42.759 --> 00:01:49.737
" Just taking the time to stop and look at the stars and look at what he created for us.

00:01:49.737 --> 00:01:51.520
It's a beautiful thing.

00:01:51.951 --> 00:01:55.741
In my prayer time, he visited me again.

00:01:56.768 --> 00:02:04.590
I don't know why I get these visitations; I make an atmosphere for him.

00:02:04.590 --> 00:02:10.280
I make a place for him to feel comfortable in my home by taking communion daily.

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:12.377
We worship him all the time.

00:02:12.377 --> 00:02:21.623
My little girl—you've never met her, I don't let her come on here, she's a little one—but she walks around praising the Lord with me.

00:02:23.320 --> 00:02:30.914
She's the one who prayed for the dog to get raised from the dead outside when I stepped on it.

00:02:32.093 --> 00:02:41.709
In this time, I was seeking the Lord concerning the lost and praying for the salvations that I've seen coming.

00:02:42.489 --> 00:02:46.790
I'm going to make this video and not worry about the time.

00:02:46.790 --> 00:02:47.480
When I'm done, I'm done.

00:02:48.170 --> 00:02:54.239
If you don't want to watch it all, that's fine, but I have to tell you what the Lord has said.

00:02:54.879 --> 00:02:59.079
I'm going to go in the direction I feel the Holy Spirit lead me.

00:02:59.299 --> 00:03:05.159
I've always been time-conscious, but not this time.

00:03:05.604 --> 00:03:13.102
I was sitting outside praying and looking at the moon because there was a big, beautiful full moon here.

00:03:14.036 --> 00:03:24.571
I was looking at the beauty of everything and talking to him about the open door.

00:03:25.524 --> 00:03:30.274
I keep praying about the open door for the lost, taking off the blinders.

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:52.217
The Lord's been revealing things to me; my wife's been reading me the books from Brother Hagin about how he prayed for the lost and how he prayed against the blinders, because the Bible says that the enemy blinds the eyes of the unsaved so they can't see.

00:03:53.760 --> 00:04:13.640
So I've been praying over the eyes of their understanding to be enlightened, just like in Ephesians, taking authority over the blinders where Satan has blinded people so they can see and have a revelation knowledge of Jesus Christ as their Lord and personal Savior.

00:04:16.1000 --> 00:04:30.027
I was interceding for the lost—that's been my goal—and for the crash and the things I've seen coming, asking the Lord to lessen it so it wouldn't be so rough on people, standing in the gap like Abraham did for Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:04:40.460 --> 00:04:45.120
Ultimately it still came, but we have authority and power to stand in the gap.

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:58.212
I was praying, interceding, "Father, I ask you to still shake and wake up the people so that we will have a great harvest of souls.

00:04:58.212 --> 00:05:08.480
" Suddenly, as I was praying over the open door, the Lord showed me a vision of a normal door on a house.

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:14.951
He said, "Brandon"—and it was like a light switch came on—he said, "Brandon, you're believing too small.

00:05:22.854 --> 00:05:27.629
I want an open door, but I want it to be a barn door.

00:05:27.935 --> 00:05:32.520
" He showed me a massive barn with both doors open.

00:05:35.887 --> 00:05:41.030
Like when you open barn doors—huge, either they slide or swing open.

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:48.000
He said, "I don't want a little 8ft door like you have in your house; I want a barn door.

00:05:53.690 --> 00:06:04.920
" He showed me a massive, humongous harvest barn, like a massive dairy farm barn, and it had two huge open doors on it.

00:06:07.981 --> 00:06:10.737
All the way through, there were two more open doors.

00:06:10.995 --> 00:06:19.919
He said, "I'm going to show you what's inside the barn: the equipment that I'm equipping the end-time army for.

00:06:25.573 --> 00:06:35.120
" I am the Lord of the harvest and I am going to harvest the souls, to harvest my people, the ones that are blinded.

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:47.509
Inside the barn, his blood was applied over it like paint.

00:06:51.180 --> 00:06:55.671
Jesus Christ's blood made a way for you to be born again.

00:06:55.671 --> 00:06:59.959
He saved you by his blood; by his stripes, you're healed.

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:06.808
He was crucified so you don't have to go to hell.

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:11.520
He showed me the barn and it was the storehouse for everything.

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:16.760
He was opening the barn doors, ready for the people to come in.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:33.742
Inside of that barn there were huge bales of massive golden hay representing the anointing and the outpouring of his spirit—a massive amount of the glory.

00:07:34.588 --> 00:07:39.070
There were glory hay bales inside of this barn.

00:07:39.535 --> 00:07:44.080
He told me, "I'm bringing forth those hay bales and it's going to bring forth the harvest.

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:45.577
This is the equipment.

00:07:45.966 --> 00:07:50.268
" The glory was going to be on the remnant, whoever's willing to be used.

00:07:56.779 --> 00:08:03.794
All of a sudden, Jesus appeared to me again, and this time he had overalls on.

00:08:05.929 --> 00:08:11.462
I said, "Lord, you have overalls on.

00:08:12.285 --> 00:08:15.040
I've never seen you wear overalls before.

00:08:15.420 --> 00:08:28.377
" He had old blue jean overalls with a white shirt underneath and a red handkerchief in the back pocket.

00:08:31.279 --> 00:08:33.799
He had a straw cowboy hat on.

00:08:35.866 --> 00:08:40.132
Some of you might say, "I don't believe that," but it's what I saw.

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:44.302
Jesus came as a harvester, an old farmer.

00:08:48.187 --> 00:08:54.720
Before him was wheat, and it was huge, ripe, and bowing down because the grains of wheat were so heavy they were bending the stalks.

00:08:56.702 --> 00:08:58.409
It was beautiful, golden ripe wheat ready to be harvested.

00:08:58.409 --> 00:09:04.859
When he walked in the midst of it, the wheat started bowing down to him.

00:09:07.307 --> 00:09:13.486
It was swaying with him as he walked in the midst of it, moving with him.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:28.359
And all of a sudden he picked one of those pieces of wheat off of the stalk and he put it in his mouth, and it just dangled there, and he smiled real big at me.

00:09:31.550 --> 00:09:33.280
He said, "Brandon, the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:42.160
I am the Lord of the harvest, and my heart is the harvest, and there will be one last harvest before I come.

00:09:43.520 --> 00:09:43.840
" And he showed me.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:47.862
He said, "I want you to see my hands.

00:09:52.245 --> 00:09:53.102
" And ladies and gentlemen, I've never seen his hands before like this.

00:10:03.450 --> 00:10:03.920
He wanted me to focus on them.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.703
And he took his hands and he put them out before me.

00:10:07.703 --> 00:10:15.880
And on his hands, there were these massive holes where he had been crucified.

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:30.658
There were big, big holes in his hands, and I could see through them.

00:10:30.658 --> 00:10:37.618
I could see the hole, and I could see through the hole and the wheat on the other side.

00:10:39.870 --> 00:10:43.789
You could see the wheat through the hole, it was so big.

00:10:43.789 --> 00:10:49.874
Now you think a little nail would be what they tacked him up there with; it was massive.

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:57.840
It was like a humongous hole, but you could see through it all the way.

00:10:58.080 --> 00:11:00.583
And I could see glory going through.

00:11:00.583 --> 00:11:09.691
It looked like glory, like a light going through him because the light was shining inside of him like his blood or whatever.

00:11:10.205 --> 00:11:13.939
It was like a glory glow, and you could see it through the hole.

00:11:13.939 --> 00:11:20.194
And whenever he held his hands out like this, I could see the wheat moving through the hole.

00:11:20.194 --> 00:11:22.560
That's how big the hole was.

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:26.870
And he said, "Brandon, I died for every single one of them.

00:11:26.870 --> 00:11:32.194
I died for all of them, and I desire that not one should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:11:32.194 --> 00:11:38.159
" And he held his hands out and he said, "Will you help me bring in the harvest?

00:11:38.159 --> 00:11:42.907
Will you help me bring in the harvest?

00:11:42.907 --> 00:11:53.700
" And I said, "Lord, as for me and my house, we will do whatever it takes to help you bring in the lost.

00:11:58.951 --> 00:12:00.818
" He says, "I know you will.

00:12:00.818 --> 00:12:01.790
" He got excited.

00:12:01.790 --> 00:12:03.890
He said, "I know you will.

00:12:03.890 --> 00:12:09.999
" And he was sitting there on the hill and he started singing me a song.

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:14.240
He started singing a lullaby to the people, and it was really private to me.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:32.310
So I'll just say he kept saying, "I am the Lord of the harvest.

00:12:51.076 --> 00:12:51.392
" He took his hands and he was telling me, "I died for them.

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:04.840
" Then he started singing me this song saying, "I am the Lord of the harvest.

00:13:05.110 --> 00:13:07.974
