00:13:24.723 --> 00:13:33.095
Through the barn, both doors were open.

00:13:33.095 --> 00:13:46.260
And whenever I told you the sun was setting on time when the last call was barely going through, you could see the sun.

00:13:46.260 --> 00:13:49.528
It was pink and beautiful and setting on time.

00:13:49.528 --> 00:13:54.200
I could see that sun again and it was barely there.

00:13:54.200 --> 00:14:00.800
It was barely just a little bit of light over the horizon of time.

00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:07.886
And he said, "Now," he said, "I'm releasing my angel armies in my reserves.

00:14:08.697 --> 00:14:19.713
The world has never seen this before, for I am releasing the angel armies to help you and to assist with this harvest.

00:14:19.713 --> 00:14:29.670
For you've never seen what's about to take place on the planet.

00:14:30.032 --> 00:14:36.920
" I saw the angel armies, and he said, "There is much more with me than there is with them.

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:40.119
" And he was pointing to the darkness.

00:14:40.119 --> 00:14:44.584
I could see the demonic forces trying to hold back the harvest.

00:14:44.584 --> 00:14:53.985
And he smiled at me and he said, "Brandon, do you know how you always quote: uninterrupted, unhindered by any satanic or demonic force?

00:14:53.985 --> 00:15:05.639
" He smiled at me and he said, "Brandon, you're about to see that in a great way: uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:15:05.639 --> 00:15:08.799
" Son, I saw the angels.

00:15:08.799 --> 00:15:26.560
There were so many angels, so many huge warring angels warring out of the sky, out of the spirit, out of the heavens, coming onto the earth, surrounding anywhere you can comprehend.

